

                       iGalFit Additional Tools
		             July 15, 2011


   iGalFit has many additional tools to facilitate the main objective of 
building, running, and analyzing GalFit input/output files.  

reginfo.pro        Display, modify, and delete the existing regions.
stretchimage.pro   Control the minimum, maximum, bias, and contrast in the 
		   image scaling.
pixhist.pro        Display the pixel histogram of the whole image, and 
		   modify the min/max settings of the display.
pixtab.pro 	   Display a pixel table as the mouse moves around the image.
editfeed.pro       Edit the GalFit FeedMe file by hand.